   <title>SenSage AP Authorization Model</title>
   <conbody>
      <p>Resource instance actions (view, edit, delete, run) act on a specific resource instance,
      either a report or dashboard. These actions are fixed and cannot be changed at run time:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <b>View</b>—Allows for viewing the resource only</li>
         <li>
            <b>Edit</b> —Allows for updates to the resource</li>
         <li>
            <b>Delete</b> —Allows for deletion of the resource</li>
         <li>
            <b>Run</b>—Allows for execution of the resource</li>
      </ul>
